'''Jimmie Kenneth Johnson''' (wavukiye [[El Cajon, muri Californiya]], ku ya 17 Nzeri 1975) ni umunyamerika wabigize umwuga.

Johnson yakinnye mu gikombe cya NASCAR kuva muri 2002 kugeza 2020 hamwe n'ikipe ya [[Hendrick Motorsports]]. Muri uru ruhererekane yatsindiye ibikombe birindwi: 2006, 2007, 2008, 2009, 2010, 2013 na 2016 kandi angana na [[Richard Petty]] na [[Dale Earnhardt]].<ref>{{cite news|last=Fryer|first=Jenna|title=Jimmie Johnson seizes record-tying 7th NASCAR championship|url=http://racing.ap.org/article/jimmie-johnson-seizes-record-tying-7th-nascar-championship|accessdate=November 20, 2016|work=Associated Press|agency=[[Associated Press]]|publisher=AP Sports|date=November 20, 2016|location=[[Homestead, Florida]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161124091427/http://racing.ap.org/article/jimmie-johnson-seizes-record-tying-7th-nascar-championship|archive-date=November 24, 2016|url-status=dead}}</ref>

Kuva mu 2021 Johnson yimukiye muri IndyCar kugirango yinjire mu ikipe ya [[Chip Ganassi Racing]].<ref>[https://au.lifestyle.yahoo.com/jimmie-johnson-will-race-in-indy-car-in-2021-and-2022-152843041.html Seven-time NASCAR Cup Series champion Jimmie Johnson will race in IndyCar in 2021 and 2022]. Yahoo Sports.</ref>

